    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't think it's growth though. it doesn't feel like i'm evolving. it just feels like everything meaningful is gone and there's nothing left to grow into. it's just... empty. like there's no point in even trying to find \"new meaning\" when the core of who i was is just dead and buried. it's exhausting to pretend otherwise.",
